channel.desc: On Graham's sofa tonight: Hollywood star Glen Powell in dystopian action thriller The Running Man; Emmy-winning Brit Rosamund Pike, in crime caper sequel Now You See Me: Now You Don't; top comic Jack Whitehall, starring in tense thriller series Malice; and music superstar Ed Sheeran, chatting and performing Camera from his album Play.
